<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net" agent="Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/130.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/130.0.0.0" version="24.7.17" scale="1" border="0"> <diagram name="PÃ¡gina-1" id="NmNGqWAuZ4Ksb0GI48bc"> <mxGraphModel dx="3428" dy="1578" grid="0" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="0" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" background="none" math="0" shadow="0"> <root> <mxCell id="0" /> <mxCell id="1" parent="0" /> <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{"data":"@startuml
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

' DOMAIN

' Define Value Objects
enum EventType {
 Wedding,
Conference,
Birthday,
FifteenBirthday,
FamilyReunion,
HolidayParty,
RetirementParty,
BBQParty,
Corporate,
Anniversary,
BabyShower,
Graduation,
BarMitzvah
}

enum ServiceType {
Catering,
Music,
Photography,
Decoration,
Videography,
AudioVisual,
FloralArrangements,
FurnitureRental,
CleanUp,
GuestAccommodation,
Bartending,
CakeDesign,
PrintingServices,
Invitations,
Entertainment,
SocialMediaPromotion,
GiftWrappings,
InteractiveActivities,
CostumeRental,
MakeUpAndHair,
Fireworks,
KidsActivities,
MassageTherapy
}

class DNI {
 - value: String
 --
 + Validate(): bool
 + Make(value: String): DNI
}

class Money {
 - amount: double
 - currency: String
 --
 + Validate(): bool
}

class Name {
 - value: String
 --
 + Validate(): bool
 + Make(value: String): Name
}

class Description {
 - value: String
 --
 + Validate(): bool
 + Make(value: String): Description
}

' Define BaseEntity class
abstract class BaseEntity {
 + id: GUID
 --
}

class EventDateTime{
 + Value: DateTime
 --
 +Make(value: DateTime): EventDateTime
 +Validate(value: String): bool
}

class EventTimeSpan{
 + StartTime: TimeSpan
 + EndTime: TimeSpan
 --
 +Make(start: TimeSpan, end: TimeSpan): EventTimeSpan
 +Validate(start: String, end: String): bool
}

' Define Classes
class Service {
 - serviceType: ServiceType
 - description: Description
 - quantity: int
 - unitCost: Money
 --
 + Make(serviceType: String, description: String, quantity: int, unitCost: double) : Service
}

class Client {
 - name: Name
 - dni: DNI
 --
 + Make(name: string, dni: string): Client
}

class Employee extends BaseEntity {
 # dni: DNI
 # salary: Money
 # task: string
 # role: String
 --
 + AssignAsManager(): Manager
 + Make(name: string, dni: string, salary: double, role: string): Employee
}

class Manager extends Employee {
 - bonus: Money
}

' Define Hall entity
class Hall extends BaseEntity {
 - name: Name
 - address: String
 - events: List<Event>
 - notAvailableDates: HashSet<Date>
 + Make(name: string, address: string): Hall
}

' Define Event entity with its methods
class Event extends BaseEntity {
 - client: Client
 - date: EventDateTime
 - time: EventTimeSpan
 - eventType: EventType
 - assignedManager: Manager
 - servicesList: List<Service>
 - totalCost: Money
 - downPayment: Money
 --
 + AddService(service: Service)
 + RemoveService(service: Service)
 + ClearServices()
 + CalculateTotalCost(): TotalCost
 + Make(client: Client, date: DateTime, startTime: TimeSpan, endTime: TimeSpan, eventType: string, assignedManager: Manager): Event
}

class ExceptionHandlingMiddleware {
 --
 + HandleException(e: Exception)
}

' INFRASTRUCTURE

' Define repositories (interfaces)
interface IEventRepository {
 + AddEvent(event: Event)
 + RemoveEvent(event: Event)
 + GetEventById(id: GUID): Event
 + GetEvents(): List<Event>
 + UpdateEvent(event: Event)
}

interface IEmployeeRepository {
 + AddEmployee(employee: Employee)
 + RemoveEmployee(employee: Employee)
 + GetEmployeeById(id: GUID): Employee
 + GetEmployeeByDNI(dni: string): Employee
 + GetEmployees(): List<Employee>
 + UpdateEmployy(employee: Employee)
}

interface IClientRepository {
 + AddClient(client: Client)
 + GetClientById(id: guid): Client
 + GetClientByDNI(dni: String): Client
 + GetClients(): List<Client>
 + UpdateClient(client: Client)
}

' APPLICATION

class EventService {
 - hall: Hall
 - eventRepository: IEventRepository
 - employeeRepository: IClientRepository
 - clientRepository: IClientRepository
 --
 + CreateEvent(eventRequest: EventRequest): Event
 + GetEventById(id: GUID): Event
 + CalceleEvent(id: GUID)
 + UpdateEvent(id: GUID, request: EventRequest)
 + GetEvents(): List<Event>
 + IsDateAvailable(date: EventDateTime): bool
}

class ClientService {
 - clientRepository: IClientRepository
 --
 + AddClient(clientRequest: ClientRequest)
 + GetClientByDNI(dni: String): Client
 + GetClients(): List<Client>
 + UpdateClient(id: GUID, request: ClientRequest)
}

class EmployeeService {
 - employeeRepository: IEmployeeRepository
 - eventRepository: IEventRepository
 --
 + AddEmployee(employeeRequest: EmployeeRequest)
 + GetEmployeeById(id: GUID): Employee
 + GetEmployees(): List<Employee>
 + GetEmployeeByRol(rol: string): Employee
 + UpdateEmployee(id: GUiD, request: EmployeeRequest)
 + RemoveEmployee(id: GUID)
}

' Requests (DTOs)

' EventRequest, ClientRequest, EmployeeRequest are records for input data
class EventRequest {
 client: Client
 date: DateTime
 startTime: TimeSpan
 endTime: TimeSpan
 eventType: EventType
 assignedManagerId: GUID
 services: List<ServiceRequest>
}

class ClientRequest {
 name: String
 dni: String
}

class EmployeeRequest {
 name: String
 dni: String
 salary: double
 task: string
 role: String
 bonus: double
}

class ServiceRequest {
 serviceType: ServiceType
 description: String
 quantity: int
 unitCost: double
}

' PRESENTATION

class ConsoleMenu {
 - eventController: EventController
 - employeeController: EmployeeController
 - clientController: ClientController
 --
 + DisplayMainMenu()
 + GetUserInput()
 + ShowEvents()
 + ShowClients()
 + ShowEmployees()
 + CreateEvent()
 + AddClient()
 + AddEmployee()
}

class EventController{
 - eventService: EventService
 - clientService: ClientService
 - employeeService: EmployeeService
 --
 + ShowMenu()
 + ShowEvents()
 + CreateEvent()
 + UpdateEvent()
 + CancelEvent()
}

class EventController{
 - employeeService: EmployeeService
 --
 + ShowMenu()
 + ShowEmployees()
 + AddEmployee()
 + UpdateEmployee()
 + DeleteEmployee()
}

class EventController{
 - clientService: ClientService
 --
 + ShowMenu()
 + ShowClients()
 + AddClient()
 + UpdateClient()
}

' Define relationships
Hall *-- Event : \"1..*\"
Hall o-- Name
Event o-- Client : \"1\"
Event o-- Manager : \"1\"
Event *-- Service : \"1..*\"
Event o-- Money
Event o-- EventDateTime
Event o-- EventTimeSpan
ExceptionHandlingMiddleware -- ConsoleMenu
Client o-- Name
Client o-- DNI
Employee o-- Name
Employee o-- DNI
Employee o-- Money
Service o-- Description
Service o-- Money
IEventRepository -- EventService
IClientRepository -- ClientService
IEmployeeRepository -- EmployeeService
EventService o-- Hall
ConsoleMenu -- EventController
ConsoleMenu -- EmployeeController
ConsoleMenu -- ClientController
EventController -- EventService
EventController -- ClientService
EventController -- EmployeeService
EmployeeController -- EmployeeService
ClientController -- ClientService

@enduml
